  ('dietitian-moex-04950', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-111-629fe76c', 'sub-dietitian-04', NULL, 'single_choice', 'TZD（thiazolidinediones）可結合於PPAR受器（peroxisomeproliferatoractivatorreceptor），用於治 療糖尿病之生化機制，下列敘述何者錯誤？', '["促進脂肪組織 PPARγ 活性而增加 PEPcarboxykinase 活性", "增加脂肪組織甘油新生（glyceroneogenesis）前驅物質的生成", "減少血液脂肪酸攝入（uptake）到脂肪組織而降低三酸甘油酯的合成", "增加GLUT4表現及提高胰島素敏感性"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:38+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "bfc5de94a4b1", "answer_pdf_sha1": "c50f93493e37", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111110", "c": "103", "s": "0201", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "生理學與生物化學", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、111年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體...", "original_question_number": 32, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-04951', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-111-629fe76c', 'sub-dietitian-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '逆向的膽固醇運送（reversecholesteroltransport）是透過那一個脂蛋白將膽固醇由週邊細胞輸送到 肝臟？', '["乳糜微粒（chylomicron）", "極低密度脂蛋白（VLDL）", "低密度脂蛋白（LDL）", "高密度脂蛋白（HDL）"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:38+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "bfc5de94a4b1", "answer_pdf_sha1": "c50f93493e37", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111110", "c": "103", "s": "0201", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "生理學與生物化學", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、111年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體...", "original_question_number": 33, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-04952', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-111-629fe76c', 'sub-dietitian-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '關於肌紅蛋白（myoglobin）攜帶氧氣的敘述，下列何者正確？', '["肌紅蛋白可攜帶氧氣，提供肌肉細胞粒線體氧化磷酸化的作用", "除了肌紅蛋白之外，含鈷離子的血藍蛋白（hemocyanin）也可以攜帶氧氣", "相較於血紅蛋白（hemoglobin），肌紅蛋白不能和一氧化碳或是氮氣結合", "每個肌紅蛋白可以攜帶8個氧氣分子"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:38+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "bfc5de94a4b1", "answer_pdf_sha1": "c50f93493e37", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111110", "c": "103", "s": "0201", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "生理學與生物化學", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、111年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體...", "original_question_number": 34, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
